==English==

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-more}}
# [[disposed|Disposed]] or [[prone]] to [[indulge]], [[humor]], [[gratify]], or [[give way]] to one's own or another's [[desire]]s, etc., or to be [[compliant]], [[lenient]], or [[forbearing]]; showing or ready to show [[favor]]; [[favorable]]; [[indisposed]] to be [[severe]] or [[harsh]], or to exercise necessary [[restraint]]: as, an indulgent parent; to be indulgent to servants.

